OL,3,CBoroughs warn homelessness is 'single
OL,4,Cbiggest risk' to council finances
OL,6,FLondon's homelessness crisis is now
OL,7,Fthe single biggest financial risk
OL,8,Ffacing local authorities, according to
OL,9,Fa new warning from London Councils.
OL,11,FThe cross-party group, which
OL,12,Frepresents the capital's 32 boroughs
OL,13,Fand the City of London, says spiraling
OL,14,Ftemporary accommodation costs have
OL,15,Fforced councils to overspend by at
OL,16,Fleast #330 million this year, an
OL,17,Fincrease of 60% when compared to
OL,18,Foriginal homelessness budgets.
