OL,3,CBoroughs warn homelessness is 'single
OL,4,Cbiggest risk' to council finances
OL,6,FCouncils are legally required to house
OL,7,Feligible homeless residents, making it
OL,8,Fessentially impossible for councils to
OL,9,Fplace strict limits on their
OL,10,Fexpenditure.
OL,12,FThe number of Londoners in temporary
OL,13,Faccommodation is now at a record high,
OL,14,Fwith 183,000 people, around one in
OL,15,Fevery 50 residents, needing shelter.
