OL,3,CBoroughs warn homelessness is 'single
OL,4,Cbiggest risk' to council finances
OL,6,FLondon Councils said the capital's
OL,7,Fboroughs are collectively spending #4
OL,8,Fmillion a day on temporary housing,
OL,9,Foften relying on costly hotel
OL,10,Fplacements due to a shortage of
OL,11,Faffordable homes.
OL,13,FOver recent years, 45,000 properties
OL,14,Fhave disappeared from the lower end of
OL,15,FLondon's private rental sector.
