OL,3,CBoroughs warn homelessness is 'single
OL,4,Cbiggest risk' to council finances
OL,6,FGrace Williams, Leader of Waltham
OL,7,FForest Council and Housing Lead for
OL,8,FLondon Councils, said: "London
OL,9,Fcouncils are facing risk of bankruptcy
OL,10,Fand homelessness is becoming the
OL,11,Fbiggest risk.
OL,13,F"They're spending #330 million
OL,14,Foverspend on homelessness on top of
OL,15,Ftheir housing budget.
OL,17,F"It's becoming a real risk of
OL,18,Fborrowers becoming bankruptcy and
OL,19,Ftherefore having to get into debt to
OL,20,Fpay for local services for Londoners."
