OL,6,FShe said: "In Waltham Forest, we spend
OL,7,F60% of our budget on adult and
OL,8,Fchildren's social care and
OL,9,Fhomelessness. That leaves less for all
OL,10,Fthe other services our residents rely
OL,11,Fon.
OL,13,F"If councils go bankrupt, they'll have
OL,14,Fto borrow more, increasing debt over
OL,15,Ftime."
