OL,3,CBoroughs warn homelessness is 'single
OL,4,Cbiggest risk' to council finances
OL,6,FLondon Councils is calling for urgent
OL,7,Faction in the upcoming government
OL,8,FSpending Review. Its demands include
OL,9,Fending the 14-year freeze on how much
OL,10,Fcouncils can claim back for temporary
OL,11,Faccommodation, making the recent
OL,12,Fuplift in Local Housing Allowance
OL,13,Fpermanent, and boosting long-term
OL,14,Finvestment in affordable housing.
OL,16,FThe group is also urging the
OL,17,Fgovernment to prioritise the cross-
OL,18,Fdepartmental strategy on homelessness
OL,19,Fand ensure councils play a central
OL,20,Frole.
