OL,3,CBoroughs warn homelessness is 'single
OL,4,Cbiggest risk' to council finances
OL,6,FA Ministry for Housing, Communities
OL,7,Fand Local Government spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "We inherited a serious housing
OL,9,Fcrisis which is why we are taking
OL,10,Furgent and decisive action to end
OL,11,Fhomelessness, fix the foundations of
OL,12,Flocal government and drive forward our
OL,13,FPlan for Change.
OL,15,F"This government is providing #1
OL,16,Fbillion for crucial homelessness
OL,17,Fservices and tackling the root causes
OL,18,Fof homelessness by building 1.5
OL,19,Fmillion new homes, boosting social and
OL,20,Faffordable housing and abolishing
OL,21,Fsection 21 no fault evictions."
